        <h2 class="text-2xl font-poppins font-bold mb-4">User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">You agree to:</p>
        <ul class="mb-6">
          <li>Provide accurate information during setup</li>
          <li>Use the service for lawful purposes only</li>
          <li>Respect the privacy and rights of other users</li>
          <li>Not interfere with the service's functionality</li>
