        <h2 class="text-2xl font-poppins font-bold mb-4">Modifications</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Users will be notified of significant changes via email or service notifications.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-poppins font-bold mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For questions about these Terms of Service, contact us at:</p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@upkeepqr.com" class="text-bright-green">legal@upkeepqr.com</a><br>
          Support: <a href="mailto:support@upkeepqr.com" class="text-bright-green">support@upkeepqr.com</a>
        </p>
  </ContentSection>

  <Footer />
</Layout>